				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\left |{\Delta } z\right | > $\end{document} 0.001 m was required, iii) evaluation of maxima was restricted to the first 0.1m behind the end of the mixer and iv) only streamlines with more than 2 maxima were considered.

